Package	Version	Description
requests	2.31.0	For sending HTTP requests to the currency exchange API.
pyttsx3	2.90	For text-to-speech functionality (offline, platform-independent).
SpeechRecognition	3.10.0	For recognizing spoken voice input using Google Web Speech API.
pyaudio	0.2.13	Required by SpeechRecognition to access the system microphone (record audio).
