On Windows, installing pyaudio might require precompiled wheels. If you get errors, use:

bash
Copy
Edit
pip install pipwin
pipwin install pyaudio
On Linux, you may need to install portaudio before installing PyAudio:

bash
Copy
Edit
sudo apt-get install portaudio19-dev
pip install pyaudio
On macOS, use:

bash
Copy
Edit
brew install portaudio
pip install pyaudio
